com.bergerkiller.bukkit.tc.attachments

Class VirtualEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bergerkiller.bukkit.tc.attachments.VirtualEntity

  • public class VirtualEntity
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a single Virtual entity, that only exists for clients using packet protocol. The entity can be spawned or destroyed for individual players.
